This is my first map.The is the final release for this map but look forward to more from me as I am just learning how to use hammer editor.I'm also not sure if the entity called "Light" is the same thing as Dynamic light.Someone told me to use dynamic lights to make it easier to see where the floors and walls end and begin.Also any tips would be used in my next map please state them in your comments.Thanks for people who download my map.

Maps that inspired this were::

Crackhouse
Texture City
Texture Final

Some great maps up there make sure you try 'em out!
